
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001/api/v1
@adminToken = <PASTE_YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE>

### Create XP Badge (Admin/Teacher only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/badges
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "XP Hunter I",
  "icon_url": "https://example.com/xp_hunter_1.png",
  "requirement_type": "XP_REACHED",
  "requirement_value": 50
}

### Create Streak Badge (Admin/Teacher only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/badges
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Daily Learner III",
  "icon_url": "https://example.com/daily_learner_3.png",
  "requirement_type": "STREAK_REACHetd",
  "requirement_value": 7
}

### Get All Badges
GET {{baseUrl}}/badges

### Get Single Badge
GET {{baseUrl}}/badges/65a2a2e2b2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2

### Update Badge (Admin/Teacher only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/badges/65a2a2e2b2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "XP Hunter II",
  "requirement_value": 100
}

### Delete Badge (Admin/Teacher only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/badges/65a2a2e2b2e2e2e2e2e2e2e2
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
